lead_paragraph: The president of the All-Russian Supporters Association (ARSA) Alexander Shprygin was arrested in Moscow on Saturday during the Russian Football Union's (RFU) conference where Vitaly Mutko was elected the organisation's president.

headline.print_headline: Russian Fans Group Leader Shprygin Arrested in Moscow
